<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title><%= @app_name %></title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Welcome to <%= @app_name %></h1>

  <p>
    This app supports two key features:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Auto-dial Numbers</strong>: Automatically place calls to phone numbers via our telephony service.
      <br>
      <%= link_to "Go to Call UI", call_path %>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Generate Blogs</strong>: Use our AI agent to create blog posts from your prompts.
      <br>
      <%= link_to "Go to Blog Generator", blog_path %>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    To get started, select one of the options above.
  </p>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> <%= @app_name %></p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
